<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>500 — LX Cloud</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-color: #050508;
      --surface: #0d0d12;
      --accent: #7c3aed;
      --accent-glow: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
      --text-primary: #ffffff;
      --text-muted: #888891;
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --font-main: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      --red: #ef4444;
      --red-glow: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.25);
      --orange: #f97316;
    }

    *,
    *::before,
    *::after {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--bg-color);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-family: var(--font-main);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* AMBIENT */
    .ambient {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .blob {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(90px);
      opacity: 0.15;
    }

    .blob.a {
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      background: var(--red);
      top: -80px;
      right: -80px;
      animation: bdrift 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    .blob.b {
      width: 380px;
      height: 380px;
      background: var(--orange);
      bottom: -80px;
      left: -60px;
      animation: bdrift 13s ease-in-out infinite alternate-reverse;
      opacity: 0.1;
    }

    .blob.c {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      background: var(--accent);
      top: 40%;
      left: 30%;
      animation: bdrift 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      opacity: 0.08;
    }

    @keyframes bdrift {
      from {
        transform: translate(0, 0)scale(1);
      }

      to {
        transform: translate(40px, 30px)scale(1.15);
      }
    }

    /* LOGO */
    .logo {
      position: fixed;
      top: 28px;
      left: 36px;
      z-index: 50;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .pip {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--red);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--red);
      animation: pip 0.6s step-end infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pip {

      0%,
      49% {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      50%,
      100% {
        opacity: 0.2;
      }
    }

    /* PAGE */
    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 72px;
      padding: 0 60px;
    }

    @media(max-width:860px) {
      .page {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 32px;
        padding: 60px 24px;
        overflow-y: auto;
        height: auto;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
    }

    /* =========================================
   RACK / SERVER — version 500 (tout fume)
   ========================================= */
    .scene {
      position: relative;
      width: 300px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .rack {
      width: 280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #130a0a 0%, #0a0808 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.12);
      border-radius: 10px 10px 6px 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.04), 0 50px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04), 0 0 40px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.06);
      padding: 14px 16px 16px;
      position: relative;
      animation: rack-shake 0.12s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes rack-shake {

      0%,
      100% {
        transform: translate(0, 0);
      }

      25% {
        transform: translate(-1px, 0);
      }

      75% {
        transform: translate(1px, 0);
      }
    }

    .rack::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -8px;
      left: 28px;
      right: 28px;
      height: 8px;
      background: #100a0a;
      border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
      border-bottom: none;
      border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
    }

    /* Toutes les unités sont en erreur */
    .ru {
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ru:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .ru-dead {
      height: 38px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1a0808, #120608);
      border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 10px;
      gap: 10px;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 16px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.06);
      animation: flicker var(--fd, 0.14s) step-end infinite;
      animation-delay: var(--fdl, 0s);
    }

    @keyframes flicker {

      0%,
      68%,
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      70% {
        opacity: 0.75;
      }

      71% {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    .ru-dead.critical {
      height: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #220a0a, #180608);
      border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.12), 0 0 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08);
      animation: flicker-crit 0.11s step-end infinite;
    }

    @keyframes flicker-crit {

      0%,
      60%,
      100% {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #220a0a, #180608);
        opacity: 1;
      }

      62% {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2e0c0c, #220808);
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      64% {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #220a0a, #180608);
        opacity: 1;
      }

      80% {
        opacity: 0.7;
      }

      82% {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    .ru-label {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 1.8px;
      color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.45);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      flex: 1;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .ru-label.crit {
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .led-r {
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--red);
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--red), 0 0 16px var(--red-glow);
    }

    .led-r.blink {
      animation: lrb var(--lb, 0.18s) step-end infinite;
      animation-delay: var(--lbd, 0s);
    }

    .led-r.blink2 {
      animation: lrb2 0.35s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes lrb {

      0%,
      49% {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      50%,
      100% {
        opacity: 0.08;
      }
    }

    @keyframes lrb2 {

      0%,
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--red), 0 0 16px var(--red-glow);
      }

      50% {
        opacity: 0.4;
        box-shadow: none;
      }
    }

    .fire-icon {
      font-size: 16px;
      animation: shake 0.45s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .fire-icon.big {
      font-size: 22px;
      animation: shake 0.3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes shake {

      0%,
      100% {
        transform: rotate(-5deg);
      }

      50% {
        transform: rotate(5deg);
      }
    }

    /* Vent */
    .vent {
      display: flex;
      gap: 3px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .vbar {
      width: 16px;
      height: 4px;
      background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    /* Heat */
    .heat {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -8px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 260px;
      height: 35px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.35) 0%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15) 40%, transparent 70%);
      animation: hpulse 0.8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    @keyframes hpulse {
      from {
        opacity: 0.6;
        transform: translateX(-50%)scaleX(1);
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(-50%)scaleX(1.25);
      }
    }

    /* SMOKE — plus dense, plus large */
    .smoke-box {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 100%;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 240px;
      pointer-events: none;
      overflow: visible;
    }

    .puff {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(155, 60, 60, 0.18) 0%, rgba(140, 140, 160, 0.14) 50%, transparent 70%);
      animation: prise var(--d) ease-out infinite;
      animation-delay: var(--dl);
      opacity: 0;
    }

    @keyframes prise {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translate(0, 0) scale(0.3);
      }

      18% {
        opacity: 0.7;
      }

      60% {
        opacity: 0.35;
        transform: translate(var(--dx), -140px) scale(1.8);
      }

      100% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translate(var(--dx2), -230px) scale(2.8);
      }
    }

    /* Beaucoup plus de puffs, venant de toute la largeur */
    .puff:nth-child(1) {
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      left: 15%;
      --d: 2.6s;
      --dl: 0s;
      --dx: -15px;
      --dx2: -28px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(2) {
      width: 55px;
      height: 55px;
      left: 30%;
      --d: 3.0s;
      --dl: 0.3s;
      --dx: 18px;
      --dx2: 30px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(3) {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      left: 45%;
      --d: 2.4s;
      --dl: 0.6s;
      --dx: -8px;
      --dx2: -20px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(4) {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      left: 60%;
      --d: 3.4s;
      --dl: 0.9s;
      --dx: 24px;
      --dx2: 38px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(5) {
      width: 65px;
      height: 65px;
      left: 75%;
      --d: 2.8s;
      --dl: 1.2s;
      --dx: -22px;
      --dx2: -36px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(6) {
      width: 45px;
      height: 45px;
      left: 22%;
      --d: 3.2s;
      --dl: 1.5s;
      --dx: 10px;
      --dx2: 18px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(7) {
      width: 72px;
      height: 72px;
      left: 50%;
      --d: 2.6s;
      --dl: 0.2s;
      --dx: -16px;
      --dx2: -25px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(8) {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      left: 65%;
      --d: 3.6s;
      --dl: 0.5s;
      --dx: 28px;
      --dx2: 42px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(9) {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      left: 8%;
      --d: 2.9s;
      --dl: 1.8s;
      --dx: -20px;
      --dx2: -35px;
    }

    .puff:nth-child(10) {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      left: 82%;
      --d: 3.1s;
      --dl: 0.8s;
      --dx: 12px;
      --dx2: 20px;
    }

    /* Sparks — partout */
    .sp {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--orange);
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--orange);
      animation: sfly var(--sd) ease-out infinite;
      animation-delay: var(--sdl);
      opacity: 0;
    }

    @keyframes sfly {
      0% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translate(0, 0)scale(1);
      }

      100% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translate(var(--sx), var(--sy))scale(0);
      }
    }

    .sp:nth-child(1) {
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      left: 18%;
      bottom: 10px;
      --sd: 0.55s;
      --sdl: 0s;
      --sx: -14px;
      --sy: -32px;
    }

    .sp:nth-child(2) {
      width: 3px;
      height: 3px;
      left: 35%;
      bottom: 14px;
      --sd: 0.5s;
      --sdl: 0.18s;
      --sx: 12px;
      --sy: -26px;
    }

    .sp:nth-child(3) {
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 6px;
      --sd: 0.7s;
      --sdl: 0.36s;
      --sx: -9px;
      --sy: -40px;
      background: var(--red);
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--red);
    }

    .sp:nth-child(4) {
      width: 3px;
      height: 3px;
      left: 65%;
      bottom: 12px;
      --sd: 0.52s;
      --sdl: 0.54s;
      --sx: 16px;
      --sy: -24px;
    }

    .sp:nth-child(5) {
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      left: 78%;
      bottom: 8px;
      --sd: 0.62s;
      --sdl: 0.72s;
      --sx: -5px;
      --sy: -34px;
      background: #fbbf24;
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px #fbbf24;
    }

    .sp:nth-child(6) {
      width: 3px;
      height: 3px;
      left: 42%;
      bottom: 16px;
      --sd: 0.48s;
      --sdl: 0.9s;
      --sx: 20px;
      --sy: -20px;
    }

    .sp:nth-child(7) {
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      left: 25%;
      bottom: 10px;
      --sd: 0.65s;
      --sdl: 1.1s;
      --sx: -18px;
      --sy: -38px;
      background: var(--red);
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--red);
    }

    /* Cables */
    .cables {
      width: 280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      height: 18px;
    }

    .cables svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      overflow: visible;
    }

    /* =========================================
   CONTENT
   ========================================= */
    .content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 420px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 7px;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: var(--red);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      width: fit-content;
      animation: badge-pulse 0.8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes badge-pulse {
      from {
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 transparent;
      }

      to {
        box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
      }
    }

    .bdot {
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--red);
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--red);
      animation: pip 0.6s step-end infinite;
    }

    .bignum {
      font-size: clamp(88px, 13vw, 128px);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 0.85;
      letter-spacing: -6px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .bignum::after {
      content: '500';
      position: absolute;
      left: 5px;
      top: 5px;
      color: var(--red);
      opacity: 0.15;
      z-index: -1;
      animation: ng 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes ng {

      0%,
      80%,
      100% {
        transform: none;
        opacity: 0.15;
      }

      82% {
        transform: translateX(-8px);
        opacity: 0.35;
      }

      85% {
        transform: translateX(5px);
        opacity: 0.22;
      }

      88% {
        transform: none;
        opacity: 0.15;
      }
    }

    .headline {
      font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 24px);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      opacity: 0.55;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* Log */
    .log {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .log::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--red), transparent);
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .log-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 12px 16px 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .wd {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .wd-r {
      background: #ff5f57;
    }

    .wd-y {
      background: #febc2e;
    }

    .wd-g {
      background: #28c840;
    }

    .log-tag {
      margin-left: auto;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      opacity: 0.4;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .log-body {
      padding: 12px 16px 14px;
    }

    .ll {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 2;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: llin 0.2s ease-out forwards;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .ll:nth-child(1) {
      animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }

    .ll:nth-child(2) {
      animation-delay: 0.5s;
    }

    .ll:nth-child(3) {
      animation-delay: 0.8s;
    }

    .ll:nth-child(4) {
      animation-delay: 1.1s;
    }

    .ll:nth-child(5) {
      animation-delay: 1.4s;
    }

    .ll:nth-child(6) {
      animation-delay: 1.7s;
    }

    @keyframes llin {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-4px);
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: none;
      }
    }

    .ok {
      color: #34d399;
    }

    .wn {
      color: #fbbf24;
    }

    .er {
      color: #f87171;
    }

    .ac {
      color: #a78bfa;
    }

    .dm {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      opacity: 0.45;
    }

    .cur {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 6px;
      height: 11px;
      background: var(--red);
      vertical-align: middle;
      margin-left: 2px;
      border-radius: 1px;
      animation: blink 0.6s step-end infinite;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      50% {
        opacity: 0;
      }
    }

    /* Button */
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 13px 28px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: var(--font-main);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      width: fit-content;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.35), 0 8px 32px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.35);
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, background 0.15s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .btn::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 55%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.55), 0 16px 48px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.5);
      background: #8b47ff;
    }

    .barrow {
      transition: transform 0.15s;
      font-size: 16px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .btn:hover .barrow {
      transform: translateX(-3px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="ambient">
    <div class="blob a"></div>
    <div class="blob b"></div>
    <div class="blob c"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="logo">
    <div class="pip"></div>LX Cloud
  </div>

  <div class="page">

    <!-- SERVER SCENE -->
    <div class="scene">
      <div style="position:relative;width:280px;margin:0 auto;">

        <!-- Smoke + sparks — beaucoup plus intenses -->
        <div class="smoke-box">
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="puff"></div>
          <div class="sp"></div>
          <div class="sp"></div>
          <div class="sp"></div>
          <div class="sp"></div>
          <div class="sp"></div>
          <div class="sp"></div>
          <div class="sp"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- RACK — tout en erreur -->
        <div class="rack">

          <div class="ru">
            <div class="ru-dead" style="--fd:0.2s;--fdl:0s;">
              <div class="fire-icon">🔥</div>
              <div class="ru-label">SRV-01 / NGINX — DEAD</div>
              <div class="led-r blink" style="--lb:0.14s;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ru">
            <div class="ru-dead critical">
              <div class="fire-icon big">🔥</div>
              <div class="ru-label crit">
                SRV-02 — KERNEL PANIC<br>
                <span style="font-size:7px;font-weight:400;opacity:0.7;">ERREUR CRITIQUE [HTTP {{ error.code }}]</span>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;">
                <div class="led-r blink" style="--lb:0.12s;--lbd:0s;"></div>
                <div class="led-r blink" style="--lb:0.12s;--lbd:0.06s;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ru">
            <div class="ru-dead" style="--fd:0.18s;--fdl:0.05s;">
              <div class="fire-icon">💨</div>
              <div class="ru-label">SRV-03 / REDIS — NO RESPONSE</div>
              <div class="led-r blink" style="--lb:0.22s;--lbd:0.1s;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ru">
            <div class="ru-dead" style="--fd:0.25s;--fdl:0.08s;opacity:0.7;">
              <div class="fire-icon">🔥</div>
              <div class="ru-label">SRV-04 / DB — TIMEOUT</div>
              <div class="led-r blink2"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ru">
            <div class="ru-dead" style="--fd:0.3s;--fdl:0.12s;opacity:0.5;">
              <div class="fire-icon">💀</div>
              <div class="ru-label">SRV-05 / BACKUP — UNREACHABLE</div>
              <div class="led-r blink" style="--lb:0.4s;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="vent">
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
            <div class="vbar"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="heat"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cables -->
        <div class="cables">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 280 18" fill="none">
            <path d="M20 2 Q60 16 100 8 Q140 0 180 14 Q220 18 260 6" stroke="rgba(239,68,68,0.22)" stroke-width="2" />
            <path d="M10 10 Q50 2 90 16 Q130 18 170 8 Q210 0 260 14" stroke="rgba(249,115,22,0.12)" stroke-width="2" />
            <path d="M30 16 Q80 3 120 15 Q160 18 200 6 Q240 0 272 12" stroke="rgba(239,68,68,0.15)"
              stroke-width="1.5" />
            <path d="M5 6 Q45 18 85 10 Q125 2 165 16 Q205 18 260 9" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)" stroke-width="2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <div class="content">
      <div class="badge">
        <div class="bdot"></div>Panne totale
      </div>
      <div class="bignum">{{ error.code }}</div>
      <div class="headline">Erreur serveur</div>
      <div class="sub">
        Le cluster entier est parti en fumée.<br>
        Nos ingénieurs ont été réveillés à 3h du matin.
      </div>

      <div class="log">
        <div class="log-bar">
          <div class="wd wd-r"></div>
          <div class="wd wd-y"></div>
          <div class="wd wd-g"></div>
          <span class="log-tag">INCIDENT LOG — CLUSTER</span>
        </div>
        <div class="log-body">
          <div class="ll"><span class="dm">00:01</span>&nbsp; <span class="ok">BOOT</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; LX-Cloud Cluster
            v4.1 — OK</div>
          <div class="ll"><span class="dm">03:47</span>&nbsp; <span class="wn">WARN</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; Charge CPU
            anormale [98%] sur SRV-02</div>
          <div class="ll"><span class="dm">03:47</span>&nbsp; <span class="er">ERROR</span>&nbsp; Kernel panic — SRV-02
            [{{ error.code }}]</div>
          <div class="ll"><span class="dm">03:47</span>&nbsp; <span class="er">CRIT</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; Cascade failure —
            SRV-01, 03, 04, 05</div>
          <div class="ll"><span class="dm">03:48</span>&nbsp; <span class="er">CRIT</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; Surchauffe
            généralisée — datacenter HS</div>
          <div class="ll"><span class="dm">03:48</span>&nbsp; <span class="dm">SOS</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ingénieurs
            alertés — intervention en cours<span class="cur"></span></div>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>

  </div>
</body>

</html>